{{Quote|If the Duchess Thax intends to strike, she'll give no warning... Rather like the Zharan glass-snake!|[[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] compares [[Duchess/Legends|Duchess]] [[Thax]] to a Zharan glass-snake|<ref name="RS">{{TCWComicCite|6.24|Runaway Starfighter}}</ref>}}
'''Zharan glass-snakes''' were creatures that wrapped around their prey.<ref name="BP">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref> During the height of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] compared [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] [[Duchess/Legends|Duchess]] [[Thax]] to the glass-snake, implying that neither provided a warning before striking.<ref name="RS" />

